description: Welcome to your Lucury 2BR/2BA condo at Echelon Seaport. South-facing 7th-floor unit overlooking a landscaped plaza and outdoor pools. Features white oak floors, open kitchen with Italian cabinetry, Thermador appliances, and spa-like marble baths. Enjoy 50,000+ sq ft of amenities, including indoor/outdoor pools, fitness facilities, basketball court, golf simulator, yoga studio, and The Club Level with lounges, dining, and outdoor terraces. Services include 24/7 concierge, valet, doormen, and porters. Echelon Seaport offers unparalleled luxury and community in Boston. Currently with a Lease till 7/1/2026. Monthly rent is 7000.00
